Reduced the serving time of the customers at Quickly which caters around 75 customers everyday
Applied DMAIC (Define, Measure, Analyze, Improve and Control) techniques to improve, optimize and stabilize their serving process
Performed Root cause analysis to identify the root cause of the delay in the food serving process
Performed Failure Mode & Effects Analysis (FMEA) and suggested ideas and recommendations to reduce defects
Used Statistical Process Control (SPC) to monitor and control the process
